collectionMetadata.name: Prohibited Drone flying areas at NParks Nature Reserves, Nature Parks and Gardens
collectionMetadata.description: The boundary of the following Nature Reserves, Nature Parks and Gardens which have prohibited drone flying within their premises: Bukit Batok Nature Park, Bukit Batok Town Park, Bukit Timah Nature Reserve, Central Catchment Nature Reserve, Chestnut Nature Park, Dairy Farm Nature Park, Hindhede Nature Park, Jurong Lake Gardens, Kranji Coastal Nature Park, Kranji Marshes, Kranji Reservoir Park, Labrador Nature Reserve (including Berlayer Creek), Lower Peirce Reservoir Park, Mandai Mudflats, Pulau Ubin, Singapore Botanic Gardens, Springleaf Nature Park, Sungei Buloh Wetland Reserve, Thomson Nature Park, Upper Peirce Reservoir Park, Upper Seletar Reservoir Park, Windsor Nature Park and Zhenghua Nature Park.
